Advance tickets may be purchased online or at the Enzian Box Office. Box Office staff will be available from 1pm-9pm daily to answer questions and assist with ticket purchases. Due to restricted theater capacity, ticket availability is limited. We highly recommend purchasing your tickets online ahead of time to guarantee your spot.
During the festival, day-of-show tickets will be available online up to 1 hour prior to showtime or in-person at the Enzian Box Office. Tickets are subject to availability.
If tickets are sold out, the show will go on standby. To gain entry to a standby film, you may queue in the ‘Standby Line’ prior to the show’s start time. At showtime, additional seats may become available and will be provided to standby guests based on queue order. We recommend arriving at the theater at least 45 minutes prior to show time to wait in the standby line.
STAFF
Enzian Theater and Florida Film Festival staff is always available to answer your questions. For information about ticketing or with general inquiries please contact the
Enzian Box Office
.
